{"tid":1034373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"還願:好多中國人話炎上其實係因為邪教比喻個中國人先至嬲","createTime":"2019-02-23T21:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T06:41:58.000Z","uid":35776,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c0d75133de7d17c03a448c9894440d3d391be468","tid":1034373,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T21:10:42.000Z","msg":"實情係過度解讀加亂咁吹風<br />\n先唔好將中國人全部面譜化<br />\nTwitter 所見炎上最大爆點係不憤被人話做邪教<br />\n只有將情況限於台灣內部先唔會過度解讀<br />\n陸心會擺到明係講愛國同心會等等班紅統同親共台灣人<br />\n膜拜中國人 相信只要拜中國人就解決到所有問題<br />\n<br />\n只係一D中國人過度解讀引戰，另一堆跟風鬧隻game先至炎上範圍越來越大，睇到嘅玩家信左對號入座先去到咁嘅狀況"},{"pid":"12603d204aa9a61d7c7c298c5681e57c655bf262","tid":1034373,"uid":35776,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T21:12:13.000Z","msg":"我知好多連登仔有玩開大陸論壇<br />\n可以嘅話番比D中國玩家知"},{"pid":"3c746c28678e39cdb9b03ab045846c68be5e87d3","tid":1034373,"uid":177089,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T01:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7bNZOaw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7bNZOaw.png&h=49e88daa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d71d1538b08d40067f39001a843af7e2632321ff","tid":1034373,"uid":23180,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T01:48:58.000Z","msg":"你玩完隻game,覺得故事好兒戲嗎？<br />\n<br />\n現實中，「還願」就是每日在上演"},{"pid":"a3b3226f693cb88236d668a7c16daaf22abda621","tid":1034373,"uid":32706,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T01:57:19.000Z","msg":"中國人，中華民族本身就同宗教信仰一樣"},{"pid":"fdbbe981465856c6201dcce0299a949e14bd31ba","tid":1034373,"uid":129739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />the chinas are very fragile"},{"pid":"45251bc6bdd05605eec0dc0fbd757d8bea9c1426","tid":1034373,"uid":12599,"like":17,"